{
  "song_name": "Because He Lives",
  "pro7_uuid": "4689DC1F-E670-491E-87B3-1D1DF80F5A67",
  "groups": [
    {
      "uuid": "C9B6DA13-2FD4-4FB6-84D1-3912B890084F",
      "name": "Verse 1",
      "slides": [
        {
          "text": "God sent His Son \nthey called Him Jesus",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        },
        {
          "text": "He came to love \nheal and forgive",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        },
        {
          "text": "He bled and died \nto buy my pardon",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        },
        {
          "text": "An empty grave \nis there to prove",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        },
        {
          "text": "My Savior lives",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "uuid": "72EEADEE-F4E6-41E8-89DD-0058A7965B9B",
      "name": "Chorus",
      "slides": [
        {
          "text": "Because He lives \nI can face tomorrow",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        },
        {
          "text": "Because He lives \nall fear is gone",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        },
        {
          "text": "Because I know \nHe holds the future",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        },
        {
          "text": "And life is worth the living\nJust because He lives",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "uuid": "155CECAD-910C-4FB9-AF0E-92EF55658BE4",
      "name": "Verse 2",
      "slides": [
        {
          "text": "How sweet to hold our newborn baby\nAnd feel the pride and joy he gives",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        },
        {
          "text": "But greater still the calm assurance\nThis child can face uncertain days",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        },
        {
          "text": "Because Christ lives",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "uuid": "7FD9F020-E0C6-4687-BF8C-037D5CA32F85",
      "name": "Verse 3",
      "slides": [
        {
          "text": "And then one day \nI'll cross that river",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        },
        {
          "text": "I'll fight life's final war with pain",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        },
        {
          "text": "And then as death \ngives way to victory",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        },
        {
          "text": "I'll see the lights of glory\nAnd I'll know He reigns",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "uuid": "44C8121A-E552-4E09-92DE-704256E19D8C",
      "name": "Tag",
      "slides": [
        {
          "text": "And life is worth the living\nJust because He lives",
          "label": "",
          "enabled": true
        }
      ]
